OL,3,CWhy cutting disability benefits will
OL,4,Cbe a nightmare for the government
OL,6,FBy Anushka Asthana, Lili Donlon-
OL,7,FMansbridge and Angus Neale
OL,9,FThe government is facing a nightmare
OL,10,Fwhen it comes to cutting the benefits
OL,11,Fbill.
OL,13,FRachel Reeves took on Conservative
OL,14,Fplans to save #3 billion by making it
OL,15,Fharder for new claimants to receive
OL,16,Fthe highest level of a health and
OL,17,Fdisability benefit.
