OL,3,CWhy cutting disability benefits will
OL,4,Cbe a nightmare for the government
OL,6,FIn the chart above the yellow bars are
OL,7,Fthe number of people expected to be
OL,8,Fmoved down the groups (from unable to
OL,9,Fwork at all into job seeking
OL,10,Fcategories) losing over #400 a month.
OL,12,FThat would reach 92,000 in this year
OL,13,Fand next and then keep growing to a
OL,14,Ftotal of 457,000 by 2029. So huge
OL,15,Fnumbers losing benefits.
OL,17,FAre most of them going to be getting
OL,18,Fback into work? The OBR doesn't think
OL,19,Fso given how tiny the pink bars are -
OL,20,Frepresenting the rise in employment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
