OL,3,CWhy cutting disability benefits will
OL,4,Cbe a nightmare for the government
OL,6,FThe court also agreed that the
OL,7,FDepartment for Work and Pensions had
OL,8,Ffailed to make adequately clear to
OL,9,Fclaimants that they were moving from a
OL,10,Fplace where they could take part in
OL,11,Fvoluntary work search activity to
OL,12,Fcompulsory work search activity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
