OL,3,CWhy cutting disability benefits will
OL,4,Cbe a nightmare for the government
OL,6,FAnd there isn't just the legal
OL,7,Fheadache.
OL,9,FThe Joseph Rowntree Foundation tracks
OL,10,Fthe experiences of people who receive
OL,11,Fdisability benefits and shared data
OL,12,Fwith us to show how they are already
OL,13,Fsuffering.
OL,15,FIt found 88% of people on the two
OL,16,Ftiers of benefit linked to the WCA say
OL,17,Fthey are going without essentials, 59%
OL,18,Fare taking loans to cover essentials
OL,19,Fand 53% are in arrears.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
